original_title: the GazettE 10TH ANNIVERSARY THE DECADE LIVE AT 03.10 MAKUHARI MESSE
overview: the GazettE's 10th anniversary memorial performance held at Makuhari Messe on March 10, 2012. This is a must-see show that includes all of the band's early representative songs such as "Wakaremichi" and "Miseinen".
title: the GazettE 10TH ANNIVERSARY THE DECADE LIVE AT 03.10 MAKUHARI MESSE
